{"name": "xtg-auth", "metadata": {"name": "xtg-auth", "version": "0.0.17", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["aiogram", "xn-auth"], "summary": "Authentication backend for Telegram Mini Apps on starlette/fastapi API", "upload_time": 1732028126}, "documentation": ["## Telegram Auth Backend for FastAPI/Starlette\n\n### INSTALL\n\nIn your FastAPI/Starlette app:\n```bash\npip install xtg-auth\n```\n\nAdd your Telegram Bot API Token to `.env` file as `TgBotToken`:\n```dotenv\nTgBotToken=0000000000:AAaaaAaAAAaaAAAAaaAAAaAAAaaAaaaaaAA\n```\n\nBefore running add AuthenticationMiddleware to your app, and set TgAuth object with passed token as backend\n```python\nfrom fastapi import FastAPI\nfrom starlette.middleware.authentication import AuthenticationMiddleware\nfrom tg_ath import TgAuth\n\napp = FastAPI()\nTOKEN = env('TgBotToken')\napp.add_middleware(AuthenticationMiddleware, backend=TgAuth(TOKEN))\n```\n\n### Using:\nProtected endpoints expect `Telegram.WebApp.initData` string in `Authorization` header afrer `Tg` prefix in each request.\n\nexample:\n```\nAuthorization: Tg user=%7B%22id%22%3A1038938370%2C%22first_name%22%3A%22Crypto%E2%86%94%EF%B8%8FFiat%22%2C%22last_name%22%3A%22%F0%9F%92%B5%F0%9F%92%B6%F0%9F%92%B3%22%2C%22username%22%3A%22ex212%22%2C%22language_code%22%3A%22en%22%2C%22allows_write_to_pm%22%3Atrue%7D&chat_instance=-6786124926491770465&chat_type=sender&auth_date=1729138692&hash=32e367eb6019007fdb2bd8f9a08628fb14ebc737df4a0dad3ecd2910b342f488 \n```\n\n---\nMade with \u2764 on top of the [X-Model](https://github.com/XyncNet/x-model) and [Aiogram](https://github.com/aiogram/aiogram).\n"], "modules": [{"name": "tg_auth", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "tg_auth.user_upsert", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "u", "type": {"name": "TgUser | WebAppUser", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "status", "type": {"name": "UserStatus", "xref": {"fqname": "tg_auth.models.UserStatus", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "user_model", "type": {"name": "type(User)", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "User", "xref": {"fqname": "tg_auth.models.User", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "tg_auth.Token", "bases": ["BaseToken"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "tg_auth.Token.user", "type": {"name": "AuthUser", "xref": {"fqname": "tg_auth.models.AuthUser", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": [{"name": "tg_auth.AuthUser", "xref": {"fqname": "tg_auth.models.AuthUser", "project": null}}, {"name": "tg_auth.BaseToken", "xref": {"fqname": "x_auth.pydantic.Token", "project": "xn-auth"}}, {"name": "tg_auth.Lang", "xref": {"fqname": "tg_auth.models.Lang", "project": null}}, {"name": "tg_auth.TgUser", "xref": {"fqname": "aiogram.types.User", "project": "aiogram"}}, {"name": "tg_auth.User", "xref": {"fqname": "tg_auth.models.User", "project": null}}, {"name": "tg_auth.UserStatus", "xref": {"fqname": "tg_auth.models.UserStatus", "project": null}}, {"name": "tg_auth.WebAppUser", "xref": {"fqname": "aiogram.utils.web_app.WebAppUser", "project": "aiogram"}}]}, {"name": "tg_auth.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "tg_auth.models.UserStatus", "bases": ["IntEnum"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "tg_auth.models.UserStatus.CREATOR", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "tg_auth.models.UserStatus.ADMINISTRATOR", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "tg_auth.models.UserStatus.MEMBER", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "tg_auth.models.UserStatus.RESTRICTED", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "tg_auth.models.UserStatus.LEFT", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "tg_auth.models.UserStatus.KICKED", "type": null, "d